    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I fixed this by disabling CSRF protection:</p>\n<pre><code>public SecurityFilterChain defaultSecurityFilterChain(HttpSecurity http)\n            throws Exception {\n        http\n                .authorizeHttpRequests((authorize) -&gt; authorize\n                        .anyRequest().authenticated())\n                // disabled only in development environment\n                .csrf(AbstractHttpConfigurer::disable);\n        return http.build();\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
